 <sect1 id="storage.docupdates.sle12_ga_maint1">
  <title>January 2015 (Documentation Maintenance Update)</title>
  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>General</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Completely restructured the manual by introducing parts.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Completely revised the complete guide.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Shortened the majority of procedures.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	The <systemitem>cciss</systemitem> driver has been replaced with the
	<systemitem>hpsa</systemitem> driver. Changed all affected paragraphs
	accordingly (Fate #316683).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.filesystems"/></term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added <xref linkend="sec.filesystems.major.btrfs.suse"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added <xref linkend="sec.filesystems.major.btrfs.quota"/> (Fate
	#315690).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added <xref linkend="sec.filesystems.major.btrfs.deduplication"/>
	(Fate #316317).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added ReiserFs to the list of file systems that can be converted to
	Btrfs (Fate #313096).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added a note on the new XFS on-disk format to <xref
	linkend="sec.filesystems.major.prealloc"/> (Fate #317042).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added <xref linkend="sec.filesystems.major.ext4"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added a note about the support status of ReiserFs to <xref
	linkend="sec.filesystems.major.reiser"/> (Fate #313799).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.resize_fs"/></term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added <xref linkend="sec.resize_fs.usecases"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added <xref linkend="sec.resize_fs.btrfs"/> (Fate #310777).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added <xref linkend="sec.resize_fs.xfs"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.lvm"/></term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Updated all parts dealing with the &yast; Partitioner, due to a new
	design and workflow. 
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added instructions on how to list physical volumes used by logical
	volumes to <xref linkend="sec.lvm.vg_resize"/> (Fate #316074).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added <xref linkend="sec.lvm.cli.lvmetad"/> (Fate #314556).
      </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.raid"/></term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Updated all parts dealing with the &yast; Partitioner, due to a new
	design and workflow. 
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added <xref linkend="sec.raid.yast.names"/> (Fate #315590).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.raid10"/></term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Removed RAID&nbsp;6 from this chapter, since setting up RAID&nbsp;6
	arrays is now supported by the &yast; partitioner.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added <xref linkend="sec.raid10.complex"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.isns"/></term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Removed all discovery domain set stuff, since this is no longer
	supported by open-isns.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.iscsi"/></term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Replaced iSCSI Target with iSCSI LIO Target.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.multipath"/></term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Restructured the whole chapter.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Removed <literal>prio_callout</literal> from <xref
	linkend="sec.multipath.policies_failover.prio"/>, since it is no
	longer supported.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added <xref linkend="sec.multipath.best_practice"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Bugfixes</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Replace ReiserFS by Ext3 for Shrinking LV (<ulink
	url="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=884287"/>). 
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	System Drops Into Emergency Shell After Enabling Multipath (<ulink url="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=889317/"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	There is no iSCSI Target in the Package List
	(<ulink url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=905239"/>).
</para></listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </sect1>
 
